"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux\" style=\"display:none\">1950–1953 war between North and South Korea</div>\n<style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r1033289096\">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}</style><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">For other conflicts and wars involving Korea, see <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Korean_battles\" title=\"List of Korean battles\">List of Korean battles</a>. For the conflict from 1945 to the present, see <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Korean_conflict\" title=\"Korean conflict\">Korean conflict</a>.</div>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1033289096\"/><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">\"6/25\" redirects here. For the date, see <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/June_25\" title=\"June 25\">June 25</a>.</div>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n\n\n</p>\n<style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r963460841\">@media all and (min-width:720px){.mw-parser-output .desktop-float-right{box-sizing:border-box;float:right;clear:right}}.mw-parser-output .infobox.vevent .status>p:first-child{margin:0}</style><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r1034237262\">.mw-parser-output .stack{box-sizing:border-box}.mw-parser-output .stack>div{margin:1px;overflow:hidden}@media all and (min-width:720px){.mw-parser-output .stack-clear-left{float:left;clear:left}.mw-parser-output .stack-clear-right{float:right;clear:right}.mw-parser-output .stack-left{float:left}.mw-parser-output .stack-right{float:right}.mw-parser-output .stack-margin-clear-left{float:left;clear:left;margin-right:1em}.mw-parser-output .stack-margin-clear-right{float:right;clear:right;margin-left:1em}.mw-parser-output .stack-m