-YoungSamMa.pdf\">\"Israel's Role in the UN during the Korean War\"</a> <span class=\"cs1-format\">(PDF)</span>. <i>Israel Journal of Foreign Affairs</i>. <b>4</b> (3): 81–89. <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doi_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Doi (identifier)\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1080%2F23739770.2010.11446616\">10.1080/23739770.2010.11446616</a>. <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"S2CID (identifier)\">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:219293462\">219293462</a>. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.israelcfr.com/documents/4-3/4-3-6-YoungSamMa.pdf\">the original</a> <span class=\"cs1-format\">(PDF)</span> on 24 August 2015.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Israel+Journal+of+Foreign+Affairs&amp;rft.atitle=Israel%27s+Role+in+the+UN+during+the+Korean+War&amp;rft.volume=4&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=81-89&amp;rft.date=2010&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1080%2F23739770.2010.11446616&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A219293462%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft.aulast=Young&amp;rft.aufirst=Sam+Ma&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.israelcfr.com%2Fdocuments%2F4-3%2F4-3-6-YoungSamMa.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKorean+War\" class=\"Z3988\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-auto-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-auto_9-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-auto_9-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-auto_9-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r999302996\"/><cite class=\"citation web cs1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https: