iew.jsp?seq=4&amp;page=1\">\"Casualties of Korean War\"</a> (in Korean). Ministry of National Defense of Republic of Korea. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.imhc.mil.kr/imhcroot/data/korea_view.jsp?seq=4&amp;page=1\">the original</a> on 20 January 2013<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">14 February</span> 2007</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Casualties+of+Korean+War&amp;rft.pub=Ministry+of+National+Defense+of+Republic+of+Korea&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imhc.mil.kr%2Fimhcroot%2Fdata%2Fkorea_view.jsp%3Fseq%3D4%26page%3D1&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKorean+War\" class=\"Z3988\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-517KWA-23\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-517KWA_23-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-517KWA_23-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-517KWA_23-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r999302996\"/><cite id=\"CITEREFEdwards2006\" class=\"citation book cs1\">Edwards, Paul M. (2006). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=5gYCm0bM68sC&amp;pg=PA517\"><i>Korean War Almanac</i></a>. Almanacs of American wars. <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infobase_Publishing\" title=\"Infobase Publishing\">Infobase Publishing</a>. p.&#160;517. <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"ISBN (identifier)\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0816074679\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0816074679\"><bdi>978-0816074679</bdi></a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">22 February</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%