\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Weng1966-251\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Weng1966_251-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r999302996\"/><cite id=\"CITEREFWeng1966\" class=\"citation journal cs1\">Weng, Byron (Autumn 1966). \"Communist China's Changing Attitudes Toward the United Nations\". <i>International Organization</i>. <b>20</b> (4): 677–704. <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doi_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Doi (identifier)\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1017%2FS0020818300012935\">10.1017/S0020818300012935</a>. <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OCLC_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"OCLC (identifier)\">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/oclc/480093623\">480093623</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=International+Organization&amp;rft.atitle=Communist+China%27s+Changing+Attitudes+Toward+the+United+Nations&amp;rft.ssn=fall&amp;rft.volume=20&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=677-704&amp;rft.date=1966&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F480093623&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1017%2FS0020818300012935&amp;rft.aulast=Weng&amp;rft.aufirst=Byron&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKorean+War\" class=\"Z3988\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-AcademyB2000-252\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-AcademyB2000_252-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r999302996\"/><cite id=\"CITEREFChinese_Military_Science_Academy2000\" class=\"citation book cs1\">Chinese Military Science Academy (September 2000).  <bdi lang=\"zh\">抗美援朝战争史</bdi> &#91;<i>History of War to Resist America and Aid Korea</i>&#93; (in Chinese). <b>I</b>. Beijing: C