rett1987135_353-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"#CITEREFPerrett1987\">Perrett 1987</a>, p.&#160;135.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-354\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-354\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"#Reference-Zaloga-1996\">Zaloga &amp; Kinnear 1996: 33–34</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-FOOTNOTERavinoCarty2003130-355\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-FOOTNOTERavinoCarty2003130_355-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"#CITEREFRavinoCarty2003\">Ravino &amp; Carty 2003</a>, p.&#160;130.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Marolda2003-356\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Marolda2003_356-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r999302996\"/><cite id=\"CITEREFMarolda2003\" class=\"citation web cs1\">Marolda, Edward (26 August 2003). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20070629131922/http://www.history.navy.mil/wars/korea/navalbattles.htm\">\"Naval Battles\"</a>. US Navy. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.history.navy.mil/wars/korea/navalbattles.htm\">the original</a> on 29 June 2007<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">22 December</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Naval+Battles&amp;rft.pub=US+Navy&amp;rft.date=2003-08-26&amp;rft.aulast=Marolda&amp;rft.aufirst=Edward&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.navy.mil%2Fwars%2Fkorea%2Fnavalbattles.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKorean+War\" class=\"Z3988\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-357\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-357\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><link rel=\"mw-dedup