.org/CorpusID:142704845\">142704845</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Critical+Asian+Studies&amp;rft.atitle=Limited+War%2C+Unlimited+Targets%3A+U.S.+Air+Force+Bombing+of+North+Korea+during+the+Korean+War%2C+1950%E2%80%931953&amp;rft.volume=44&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=467-92&amp;rft.date=2012&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1080%2F14672715.2012.711980&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A142704845%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft.aulast=Kim&amp;rft.aufirst=Taewoo&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKorean+War\" class=\"Z3988\"></span>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-374\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-374\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r999302996\"/><cite id=\"CITEREFWard_Thomas2001\" class=\"citation book cs1\">Ward Thomas (14 June 2001). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.org/details/ethicsofdestruct00thom/page/149\"><i>The Ethics of Destruction: Norms and Force in International Relations</i></a>. <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cornell_University_Press\" title=\"Cornell University Press\">Cornell University Press</a>. p.&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.org/details/ethicsofdestruct00thom/page/149\">149</a>. <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"ISBN (identifier)\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0801487415\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0801487415\"><bdi>978-0801487415</bdi></a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Ethics+of+Destruction%3A+Norms+and+Force+in+International+Relations&amp;rft.pages=149&amp;rft.pub=Cornell+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2001-06-14&amp;rft.i