ocus.org-380\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-japanfocus.org_380-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-japanfocus.org_380-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-japanfocus.org_380-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r999302996\"/><cite id=\"CITEREFArmstrong2010\" class=\"citation journal cs1\">Armstrong, Charles (20 December 2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.japanfocus.org/-charles_k_-armstrong/3460/article.html\">\"The Destruction and Reconstruction of North Korea, 1950–1960\"</a>. <i>The Asia-Pacific Journal</i>. <b>8</b> (51).</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Asia-Pacific+Journal&amp;rft.atitle=The+Destruction+and+Reconstruction+of+North+Korea%2C+1950%E2%80%931960&amp;rft.volume=8&amp;rft.issue=51&amp;rft.date=2010-12-20&amp;rft.aulast=Armstrong&amp;rft.aufirst=Charles&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.japanfocus.org%2F-charles_k_-armstrong%2F3460%2Farticle.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKorean+War\" class=\"Z3988\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-381\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-381\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r999302996\"/><cite id=\"CITEREFKiernanOwen2015\" class=\"citation journal cs1\"><a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ben_Kiernan\" title=\"Ben Kiernan\">Kiernan, Ben</a>; Owen, Taylor (27 April 2015). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://apjjf.org/2015/13/16/Ben-Kiernan/4313.html\">\"Making More Enemies than We Kill? Calculating U.S. Bomb Tonnages Dropped on Laos and Cambodia, and Weighing Their Implications\"</a>. <i>The Asia-Pacific Journal</i>. <b>13</b> (17)<span class=\"reference-accessdate\