 2002). \"<span class=\"cs1-kern-left\">\"</span>No Practical Capabilities\": American Biological and Chemical Warfare Programs During the Korean War\". <i>Perspectives in Biology and Medicine</i>. <b>45</b> (2): 241–49. <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doi_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Doi (identifier)\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1353%2Fpbm.2002.0024\">10.1353/pbm.2002.0024</a>. <a href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PMID_(identifier"